-♪ GONNA BE A STANDOFF

22:19.512 --> 22:21.862
-CARLOS! CARLOS, DON'T.

22:34.614 --> 22:35.876
LET GO.

22:46.495 --> 22:47.714
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

22:49.803 --> 22:52.240
-I THOUGHT I SPOTTED ONE OF THE
GANG BANGERS THAT MUGGED HOBIE.

22:53.154 --> 22:54.198
I WAS CHECKING HER OUT.

22:55.678 --> 22:57.376
-WELL, WHAT HAPPENED?
WAS IT HER?

22:59.029 --> 23:00.335
-YEAH.

23:01.162 --> 23:02.816
-WELL, WHY DIDN'T
YOU TELL GARNER?

23:05.209 --> 23:06.515
-'CAUSE SHE'S MY SISTER.

23:12.086 --> 23:14.001
-YOU KNEW SHE WAS
HANGING OUT HERE.

23:16.003 --> 23:17.613
THAT'S WHY YOU CALLED MITCH

23:17.744 --> 23:19.572
TO SEE IF THERE WERE ANY
SPOTS OPEN AT BAYWATCH, RIGHT?

23:21.051 --> 23:22.705
-HER BOYFRIEND BROUGHT
HER INTO HIS GANG.

23:22.836 --> 23:24.185
WHEN I FOUND OUT I
PROMISED MY PARENTS

23:24.315 --> 23:25.708
I'D BRING HER BACK.

23:25.839 --> 23:27.057
-WELL, WHY DIDN'T YOU
TELL US ABOUT HER?

23:27.188 --> 23:28.450
-BECAUSE IT WASN'T
YOUR PROBLEM.

23:28.581 --> 23:29.756
-WELL, IT IS NOW.

23:29.886 --> 23:31.322
-WELL, HOW DO YOU THINK I FEEL?

23:31.453 --> 23:33.020
I CAN'T EVEN LOOK
MITCH IN THE EYE

23:33.150 --> 23:34.674
AFTER WHAT MY SISTER
DID TO HIS SON.

23:38.068 --> 23:39.287
LOOK, I'M SORRY.

23:39.418 --> 23:40.723
I SHOULD'VE BEEN
UP FRONT WITH YOU,

23:40.854 --> 23:42.246
BUT I DIDN'T THINK
I'D NEED ANY BACKUP.

23:43.683 --> 23:45.772
-WORST MISTAKE A
LIFEGUARD CAN MAKE.

23:47.817 --> 23:48.992
[SIGH]

24:12.102 --> 24:13.452
-BYE, MOM.

24:13.582 --> 24:15.062
[SPEAKS SPANISH]

25:19.518 --> 25:20.910
-STEPHANIE: CARLOS!

25:33.880 --> 25:35.316
-THANKS.

25:35.446 --> 25:36.578
-WELL, THERE'S NOTHING
LIKE A GOOD WORKOUT

25:36.709 --> 25:38.537
TO GET YOUR MIND
OFF YOUR PROBLEMS.

25:38.667 --> 25:41.235
-YEAH, WELL, UNFORTUNATELY
THEY ALL COME RUSHING BACK

25:41.365 --> 25:42.802
ONCE YOU GET OUT OF THE WATER.

25:44.717 --> 25:48.111
YOU KNOW, EVERY TIME I
SEE MY MOTHER AND FATHER

25:48.242 --> 25:50.679
IT REMINDS ME ABOUT
HOW ASHAMED I AM

25:50.810 --> 25:52.246
FOR EVERYTHING THAT
I PUT THEM THROUGH.

25:53.943 --> 25:56.380
AND NOW WITH ADELSA, IT'S
LIKE I'M RESPONSIBLE.

25:56.511 --> 25:57.556
SHE LEARNED FROM ME.

25:58.557 --> 26:00.646
I'M PUTTING THEM THROUGH THAT
SAME HELL ALL OVER AGAIN.

26:00.776 --> 26:02.343
-YOU WERE IN A GANG?

26:02.473 --> 26:03.605
-LET'S JUST SAY IT'S
KINDA HARD TO BE A SAINT

26:03.736 --> 26:04.954
GROWING UP IN THE CITY.

26:08.131 --> 26:10.525
BUT IT'S DIFFERENT
FOR THESE KIDS NOW.

26:10.656 --> 26:13.267
THERE'S A LOT MORE ANGER
AND RESENTMENT OUT THERE.

26:15.791 --> 26:17.271
AND A LOT LESS HOPE.

26:18.794 --> 26:20.840
BUT THE BIGGEST DIFFERENCE
IS, WHEN WE HAD A BEEF,

26:20.970 --> 26:22.798
WE SETTLED THINGS
WITH OUR FISTS.

26:24.104 --> 26:25.496
NOW THEY USE GUNS.

26:27.324 --> 26:28.630
OH WELL.

26:30.893 --> 26:32.591
WELCOME TO THE '90S.

26:34.375 --> 26:35.855
-SO, WHAT'S GONNA
HAPPEN TO ADELSA?

26:35.985 --> 26:37.378
-MY PARENTS ARE SENDING HER UP

26:37.508 --> 26:39.075
TO LIVE WITH RELATIVES
IN SANTA BARBARA.

26:40.337 --> 26:42.165
JUST LIKE THEY DID WITH ME.

26:42.296 --> 26:45.168
-WELL, SOMETIMES THE
BEST THING FOR A PERSON

26:45.299 --> 26:46.735
IS A CHANGE OF SCENE.

26:47.780 --> 26:48.737
-YEAH.

26:49.869 --> 26:51.261
HAVE YOU EVER BEEN
TO SANTA BARBARA?

26:51.392 --> 26:52.698
-YEAH.

26:52.828 --> 26:55.004
-THE BEACHES ARE
BEAUTIFUL UP THERE.

26:55.135 --> 26:57.093
CLEAN AND UNSPOILT.

26:57.224 --> 26:59.356
THAT WAS THE FIRST TIME
I EVER WENT IN THE OCEAN.

26:59.487 --> 27:01.228
I WAS 16 YEARS OLD.

27:01.881 --> 27:03.534
MY UNCLE HAD TO
TEACH ME HOW TO SWIM.

27:03.665 --> 27:06.407
-[LAUGHS] WELL, I'D SAY HE
WAS A PRETTY GOOD TEACHER.

27:06.537 --> 27:07.887
-YEAH, HE WAS.

27:08.757 --> 27:10.716
HE OPENED UP A WHOLE
NEW WORLD FOR ME.

27:11.760 --> 27:13.849
FROM THEN ON, I WAS A
TOTALLY DIFFERENT PERSON.

27:15.329 --> 27:17.766
HE MADE ME REALIZE THAT
I HAD OPTIONS IN MY LIFE.

27:18.637 --> 27:21.030
THAT I COULD MAKE
SOMETHING OF MYSELF.

27:23.337 --> 27:26.166
WELL, NOW THAT I'VE TOLD
YOU MY WHOLE LIFE STORY,

27:26.296 --> 27:27.167
LET'S HEAR YOURS!

27:27.297 --> 27:28.690
[LAUGHS]

27:28.821 --> 27:32.302
OH, COME ON, LIEUTENANT
STEPHANIE HOLDEN!

27:32.433 --> 27:34.565
I WANT TO HEAR ALL
ABOUT YOUR SORDID PAST.

27:34.696 --> 27:35.915
-OH, FORGET IT.

27:36.045 --> 27:37.699
-WAIT A MINUTE, WAIT A MINUTE.

27:37.830 --> 27:39.353
I SPILLED MY GUTS AND
YOU DON'T SAY A WORD?

27:39.483 --> 27:40.354
THAT'S NOT FAIR.

27:40.484 --> 27:42.356
[LAUGHS]

27:42.486 --> 27:44.358
HOW ARE WE SUPPOSED TO
GET TO KNOW EACH OTHER?

27:48.971 --> 27:50.538
-WELL, YOU COULD ASK ME OUT.

28:03.377 --> 28:07.990
