40:31.777 --> 40:33.996
-WHOA. THAT'S AWESOME!

40:34.997 --> 40:36.608
SO TELL ME, HOW'D
YOU DO THAT TRICK

40:36.738 --> 40:38.348
WITH THE CHAINS IN THE WATER?

40:38.479 --> 40:39.872
-OH, I'M SORRY, HOBIE,
I COULDN'T POSSIBLY

40:40.002 --> 40:41.656
TELL YOU HOW I DID MY
DEATH-DEFYING FEAT.

40:41.787 --> 40:43.049
-I'LL TELL YOU HOW HE DID IT.

40:43.179 --> 40:44.529
-HOW?

40:44.659 --> 40:45.660
-MAGIC.

40:45.791 --> 40:46.835
-OH, COME ON, REALLY. TELL ME.

40:46.966 --> 40:48.663
-MAGIC!

40:48.794 --> 40:50.448
WITH A LITTLE HELP
FROM A MERMAID.

40:51.449 --> 40:52.624
-A MERMAID, SURE.

40:52.754 --> 40:54.669
I'M OUT OF HERE,
YOU GUYS ARE NUTS!

40:54.800 --> 40:57.150
-HEY, THANKS FOR NOT
KILLING THE ILLUSION.

40:57.280 --> 40:58.891
-WELL, LIKE I SAID BEFORE,

40:59.021 --> 41:00.022
MY LIPS ARE SEALED.

41:00.806 --> 41:02.068
-WELL, WOULD YOU
MIND UNSEALING THEM

41:02.198 --> 41:03.939
FOR A MOMENT SO I CAN
GIVE YOU A GOODBYE KISS?

41:04.070 --> 41:05.158
IF YOU DON'T MIND.

41:06.551 --> 41:08.422
-I DON'T MIND AT ALL.

